,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-27T20:18:35.000Z","msg":"有啲icon香港psstore都冇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0bfdbbde3077d6ac47b3a5b276960e2142b5838d","tid":259990,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:34:59.000Z","msg":"server狂disconnect<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過好彩係steam買只係2XX<br />\n<br />\n學美國賣$40我可能唔會買"},{"pid":"6a99a4a17fc275f768a675e1bfca289f0f1f27f5","tid":259990,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:37:36.000Z","msg":"同類遊戲dead by daylight design得好好多"},{"pid":"225b790c9ee5d0f6492b932698f4de242b861b45","tid":259990,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T05:50:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同類遊戲dead by daylight design得好好多</blockquote><br />\n各有各好<br />\n<br />\n本身毒開可以玩番DBD<br />\n<br />\n鐘意吹水玩野挑戰生存難度，呢隻都可以一試<br />\n<br />\n香港區賣20-30蚊美金算合理<br />\n<br />\n40就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"403c6494c621aaa51401881ad42cef541afce59a","tid":259990,"uid":14812,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:01:04.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>同類遊戲dead by daylight design得好好多</blockquote><br />\n各有各好<br />\n<br />\n本身毒開可以玩番DBD<br />\n<br />\n鐘意吹水玩野挑戰生存難度，呢隻都可以一試<br />\n<br />\n香港區賣20-30蚊美金算合理<br />\n<br />\n40就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩隻都買左<br />\ndead by daylight 多好多野玩 成個FEEL都緊張好多<br />\n依隻歡樂d搞笑d 不過比較快悶"},{"pid":"c22929f7c04ac55c56b723e92035a4d5e2d0097a","tid":259990,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T06:23:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>同類遊戲dead by daylight design得好好多</blockquote><br />\n各有各好<br />\n<br />\n本身毒開可以玩番DBD<br />\n<br />\n鐘意吹水玩野挑戰生存難度，呢隻都可以一試<br />\n<br />\n香港區賣20-30蚊美金算合理<br />\n<br />\n40就不了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n兩隻都買左<br />\ndead by daylight 多好多野玩 成個FEEL都緊張好多<br />\n依隻歡樂d搞笑d 不過比較快悶</blockquote><br />\n係，易死(雖然夾番套戲係合理)，變相太多時間係睇人玩(咁不如我去睇人直播算)<br />\n<br />\n個人覺得一場20分鐘時間太長<br />\n<br />\n第一個頭幾分鐘死左，又要等晒成場完先有500 exp，我現在係PS4玩Fifa同呢隻game交換住咁玩黎燒時間<br />\n<br />\n可以濃縮到15分鐘一場，加多D位比人call tommy，同比早死果D玩家5分鐘就有完場果500 exp會合理D<br />\n<br />\n隻game出左幾日我諗都要比時間人地patch下，不過最緊要係搞番好個server先，亞洲區普遍2XX ping真係唔係路<br />\n<br />\n始終細studio產品，香港個價錢都合理嘅"},{"pid":"26ed6416bfc454d7a7e5d06cb9682338c81a5b97","tid":259990,"uid":80,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-29T13:26:53.000Z","msg":"易死又唔知算唔算易死<br />\n<br />\n識玩既一定用AJ mason stealth 10/10 同唔會咁易fear比人搵到<br />\n<br />\n俄區steam唔洗1舊水 抵屌"},{"pid":"a7c6f96ffc9222f222a52b44e54db1301947fce2","tid":259990,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-05-30T06:53:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>易死又唔知算唔算易死<br />\n<br />\n識玩既一定用AJ mason stealth 10/10 同唔會咁易fear比人搵到<br />\n<br />\n俄區steam唔洗1舊水 抵屌</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n睇對手，隻game本身就係要你控制fear<br />\n<br />\n有D識玩jason嘅一開始就識打爛電箱製造恐慌、有效運用自己技能、破壞生存者逃生方法<br />\n<br />\n生存者亦用自己策略去應對，呢個就係樂趣之處，係一局有時長左少少令人覺得悶<br />\n<br />\n根本呢幾日玩熟左都唔少人掌握左生存方法<br />\n<br />\n我係見D人成日投訢Jason op就覺得<br />\n<br />\n「你不如去多D理解下隻game先啦」<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"625e2542955d8e7690b328a7e7f05682b17e0740","tid":259990,"uid":76754,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-01T15:30:23.000Z","msg":"我買左<br />\n但成日searching 成10分鐘都入唔到房玩<br />\n有時就好快有<br />\n唔知係咪我問題？"},{"pid":"51e76b13b170bbe71f673cbf02516998573500df","tid":259990,"uid":23180,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-02T13:08:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我買左<br />\n但成日searching 成10分鐘都入唔到房玩<br />\n有時就好快有<br />\n唔知係咪我問題？</blockquote><br />\n我ISP netvigator<br />\n<br />\n通常search 2-3分鐘就有lobby，不過係PC版<br />\n<br />\nPS情況就唔清楚，不過呢幾日主機版個server就仲整緊:<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/Fridaythe13thGame/posts/178387